  rintros b ‚ü®hb‚ÇÅ, hb‚ÇÇ‚ü©,
  refine le_antisymm hb‚ÇÅ (closure_lt_subset_le hg hf _),
  convert hb‚ÇÇ using 2, simp only [not_le.symm], refl
end

