  refine Œª Œµ Œµ_pos, ‚ü®(Œµ/(2 * (1 + abs x)), 1), ‚ü®div_pos Œµ_pos hx, zero_lt_one‚ü©, _‚ü©,
  suffices : ‚àÄ (a b : Œ±), abs a < Œµ / (2 * (1 + abs x)) ‚Üí abs (b - x) < 1 ‚Üí (abs a) * (abs b) < Œµ,
  by simpa only [and_imp, prod.forall, mem_prod, ‚Üê abs_mul],
  intros a b h h',
